You sure are serious about this.

329
00:19:29,860 --> 00:19:29,890
You sure are serious about this.

330
00:19:30,490 --> 00:19:33,200
I know, let's go upstairs!

331
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:35,250
I'll introduce you to my friends!

332
00:19:39,300 --> 00:19:40,120
It's a turtle!

333
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:42,950
SEA
TURTLE

334
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:42,950
It says "Sea Turtle Elevator".

335
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,660
Turtle-chin.  Take us up, please.

336
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:54,710
These are the underwater Coral Apartments.

337
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:57,800
My room is on the lowest floor, since it's the cheapest.

338
00:19:57,800 --> 00:20:01,070
The highest levels, where the sun shines,
are the most expensive.

339
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,010
Are you poor?

340
00:20:04,010 --> 00:20:06,010
By the way, what about Hachi and Pappagg?

341
00:20:06,010 --> 00:20:09,010
Hacchin got badly injured about a year ago.

342
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:13,840
Yeah.  He was protecting the Sunny
on the Sabaody Archipelago, wasn't he?

343
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:17,320
I heard that his injuries have more or less healed,

344
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:21,460
but Hacchin was originally a resident of
the Fishman District, so he's recovering there.

345
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,700
Fishman District?

346
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:29,910
It's kind of a scary place, but if you guys
are with me, I don't mind giving you a tour.

347
00:20:29,910 --> 00:20:33,470
Let's go there after!
I have to meet Hachi and thank him, after all.

348
00:20:33,470 --> 00:20:35,220
Sure, I got it.

349
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:38,060
Uh... And as for Pappagg...

350
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:41,100
He's a super-famous designer,

351
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:46,450
so he's got a huge mansion in Fishverly Hills, the most luxurious part of Fishman Island!

352
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:49,940
I'm going there to deliver clams for him today.
Why don't you come along?

353
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:51,760
Aren't you his owner?

354
00:20:52,370 --> 00:20:54,110
Why don't you live together?

355
00:20:55,280 --> 00:20:58,430
I don't really fit in there.

356
00:20:58,890 --> 00:21:01,370
And the clams in these parts taste better anyway.

357
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:05,160
Hey, what's that straw-like thing?

358
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,450
Oh, that's...

359
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:10,240
the Water Road, created by
the bubble craftsmen of the island.

360
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:13,480
The fishes and merfolk like me ride it.

361
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:15,820
Just watch!

362
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:24,620
We've reached the surface!

363
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:27,590
Look!  I can even swim through the sky!

364
00:21:28,730 --> 00:21:30,060
That looks fun!

365
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:30,980
Huh?

366
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:36,080
Hey, wait!  More importantly,
there are clouds and a sky here in the deep sea!

367
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:38,200
Hey, Caimie!

368
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:40,090
That was a woman's voice!

369
00:21:40,770 --> 00:21:42,490
Everyone!

370
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:47,780
Are your friends alright now?
The pirates who drowned, I mean.

371
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:53,850
You're the ones who
didn't come through the entrance, right?

372
00:21:56,330 --> 00:21:59,580
Hello.  You don't look too scary.

373
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:03,910
Illegal immigrants?  How wild!  I really like pirates.

374
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:08,680
It's almost like a fairy tale world!

375
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:12,750
The coral continent!  The mermaids' bay!

376
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:17,480
Sanji is sobbing?!

377
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:20,550
He's crying harder than he did when he left the Baratie.

378
00:22:23,220 --> 00:22:25,570
I've finally found it!

379
00:22:26,360 --> 00:22:29,600
This is my All Blue!

380
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:34,460
Are you really sure about that, Sanji?

381
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:37,610
I'll introduce them to you.

382
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:40,280
This is Luffy-chin, the captain!

383
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:42,720
The crying one is Sanji-chin!

384
00:22:43,220 --> 00:22:44,650
And this is Usopp-chin with the nose!

385
00:22:44,980 --> 00:22:46,700
Chopper-chin the raccoon dog!

386
00:22:47,340 --> 00:22:48,320
I'm a reindeer!

387
00:22:49,190 --> 00:22:51,620
What's wrong?  Why are you crying?

388
00:22:53,510 --> 00:22:56,860
Welcome!  Let's dance together in the ocean!

389
00:23:01,850 --> 00:23:04,380
Oh... I understand now.

390
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:07,050
There's no way such joy could exist.

391
00:23:07,050 --> 00:23:09,920
I must have died today.

392
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:11,770
Negative!

393
00:23:11,770 --> 00:23:14,830
Seriously, what happened to you during the past two years?!

394
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:18,140
This island is the paradise
you've always dreamed of, right?!

395
00:23:19,290 --> 00:23:22,410
Sanji, you're so funny!

396
00:23:23,770 --> 00:23:28,320
This barrel washed ashore with Caimie's friends.
I wonder what's inside it?

397
00:23:28,320 --> 00:23:30,300
Alcohol?  Treasure?

398
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:34,520
Who knows... It's sealed pretty tight, though.

399
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:37,940
What do you think?  Should we secretly open it?

400
00:23:45,320 --> 00:23:48,020
So Straw Hat Luffy...

401
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:50,370
{\an8}has finally come here?

402
00:23:48,740 --> 00:23:50,370
Fishman District "Noah"

403
00:23:51,310 --> 00:23:52,370
Yeah...

404
00:23:52,370 --> 00:23:56,370
W-What should we do, boss?

405
00:23:58,590 --> 00:24:02,920
Bring him here... to me.

